      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I get that, but it's not just about server space. The audit showed that the Neural-Symbolic engine is way more efficient and handles formal logic much better than the current LLM framework. The company thinks it'll reduce translation errors in our financial and legal sectors significantly. It's a much more stable long-term solution.",
